name: Coco Mademoiselle Parfum
description: Coco Mademoiselle Parfum by Chanel is a Amber Floral fragrance for women. Top notes are Bergamot, Orange and Grapefruit.

name: Kenzo Jungle Le Tigre
description: Kenzo Jungle le Tigre by Kenzo is a Amber Spicy fragrance for women. Top notes are Kumquat, Tangerine and Orange.

name: Versace Eros
description: Eros by Versace is a Aromatic Fougere fragrance for men. Top notes are Mint, Green Apple and Lemon.

name: Bleu de Chanel
description: Bleu de Chanel by Chanel is a Woody Aromatic fragrance for men. Top notes are Grapefruit, Lemon, Mint and Pink Pepper.

name: Park Avenue Euphoria
description: The premium scent of Park Avenue Conquer gives the wearer unique and intense confidence of ruling the room with their mere presence.

name: Black Opium Eau De Parfum
description: Black Opium Eau de Parfum is a modern glam rock version of a classic feminine scent. A Warm and spicy fragnance with coffee, white flowers and vanilla.

name: Davidoff Cool Water EDT
description: Cool Water is fresh and sharp, simple and very masculine. Top notes include mint and green nuances, lavender, coriander and rosemary.
